Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.29,0:13:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}ん…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.83,0:13:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}美姫の友達？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.92,0:13:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}あ そう…
